CODE MANIPULATION\
\
Filtered through out the code you will see the simple code for the "Light an LED" example provided on Arduino.com. The main part to really note, is I changed some of the Choreo code near the bottom, so that 'while a tweet is available the serial monitor will print AND an LED will light up'.\
